Package: rivalcfg-gui
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-gi, python3-cairo, python3-rivalcfg, python3-evdev, python3-pynput, python3-xlib
Description: GTK3 GUI configuration tool for SteelSeries mice (via rivalcfg)
 RivalCFG GUI is a Linux desktop application for configuring
 SteelSeries mouse settings including DPI, polling rate,
 RGB lighting, and button mappings through a modern GTK3 interface.
 Works with all devices supported by the rivalcfg CLI tool.
